{{Nepali Congress}} '''Nepal Woman Association''' is the woman wing of [[Nepali Congress]].
==History== Nepal Woman Association was formed by [[Mangala Devi Singh]], the pioneer of Nepalese woman movement. It is the first female political organization of Nepal.
