[[File:Time is money, Efficiency is life.jpg|thumb|The slogan was made a large sign at the junction of [[Nanhai Boulevard]], Taizi Road and Gongye 1st Road, [[Shekou]], ]] "'''Time is Money, Efficiency is Life'''" (Chinese:"'''时间就是金钱，效率就是生命'''") is a widespread slogan of China's [[Economic reform in China|economic reform]]. It was initially a quote from [[Yuan Geng]] made in 1981.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://english.cri.cn/3126/2008/10/31/53s419849.htm | title=Time is Money, Efficiency is Life | accessdate=17 July 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://en.ce.cn/subject/Shenzhen%20SEZ/ShenzhenSEZt/201008/27/t20100827_21769263.shtml | title=1982: "Time is Money, Efficiency is Life" | accessdate=17 July 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.china.com.cn/economic/zhuanti/ggkf30/2008-10/16/content_16621796.htm | title=时间就是金钱，效率就是生命 | accessdate=17 July 2016}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web | url=http://xian.qq.com/a/20090903/000276.htm | title=时间就是金钱效率就是生命 | accessdate=17 July 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://sztv.cutv.com/shenzhen/201202/1025668210.shtml | title=时间就是金钱 效率就是生命 | accessdate=17 July 2016}}</ref>
